oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Map of the Front Lines of 3rd Division on the Marne, May 31 to July 29
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This map shows the daily front line positions of units in the 3rd Division on the Marne River sector east of Paris during the period from May 31 to July 29, 1918. The map shows American Army positions along the Marne near the village of Chateau-Thierry in June and July of 1918.
